snippet: Andreas Schockenhoff, a well-known critic of Russia, died last weekend of heart failure or heat exposure, an autopsy showed.
abstract: Medical examiners say they have ruled out foul play in death of German politician Andreas Schockenhoff, well-known critic of Russia.
lead_paragraph: Andreas Schockenhoff, a well-known critic of Russia, died last weekend of heart failure or heat exposure, an autopsy showed.

headline.main: Foul Play Ruled Out in German Politician’s Death
headline.print_headline: Germany: Politician Critical of Putin Died of Natural Causes, Autopsy Finds
